•   Enter UPI PIN on UPI PIN page only.
  •   Never share UPI PIN with anyone.
  •   Do not share your card details and OTP.
  •   Do not authorize unknown UPI Payment Links.
  •   Always verify the UPI ID of the person before payment.
  •   You do not need to enter UPI PIN to receive money.
  •   Scanning QR is for sending money, not for receiving money.
  •   Do not respond to unknown UPI Collect Requests.
  •   Check SMS when money is deducted.
  •   Beware of Phishing! Always download BHIM AXIS PAY from official website/App Store links. Do not sideload.
  •   For more details, please visit https://www.axisbank.com/bank-smart/safe-banking
